('juno-hair-garosugil', 'JUNO HAIR Garosugil', '준오헤어 가로수길점', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Garosugil', '서울 강남구 신사동 가로수길', 'Hair salon', 'Garosugil branch of Seoul''s largest salon chain — a reliable first cut, with 50+ Klook bookings.', 'As the Garosugil branch of Seoul''s largest salon chain, it offers the kind of predictability that matters on a first visit, and more than fifty bookings have already come through Klook.', 'a reliable first haircut in Seoul', 'JUNO HAIR''s Garosugil branch sits on Garosugil in Sinsa-dong, Gangnam, and belongs to Seoul''s largest salon chain. The offering is straightforward hair styling, and the branch has logged more than fifty bookings through Klook — a useful signal if you are weighing where to book a first appointment.

The chain maintains a website at junohair.com and a main Instagram account, @junohair_official. Booking ahead through Klook is the simplest route in.', null, null, 'https://junohair.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/junohair_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=JUNO%20HAIR%20Garosugil%20%EA%B0%80%EB%A1%9C%EC%88%98%EA%B8%B8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%A4%80%EC%98%A4%ED%97%A4%EC%96%B4%20%EA%B0%80%EB%A1%9C%EC%88%98%EA%B8%B8%EC%A0%90', true),
('color-place-k-pop-celeb-personal-color', 'Color Place', '컬러플레이스 (강남)', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangnam', '서울 강남구', 'Personal color analysis', 'The K-pop celebrity personal-color studio — famous for idol visits, from BLACKPINK to TWICE.', 'The client list is the credential — idols from BLACKPINK to TWICE have visited, and 202 reviews hold the rating at a flat 5.0.', 'K-pop fans seeking an idol-visited studio', 'Color Place is the Gangnam studio best known for its K-pop clientele — idols from BLACKPINK to TWICE have visited for personal-color analysis, and it holds a 5.0 rating across 202 reviews. The service is a single specialty, color diagnosis, offered under a brand with a considerable public profile: an official site at colorplace.co.kr and an Instagram following of more than fifty thousand at @colorplace_official. Check the website for session details and booking before you go.', 5, 202, 'https://colorplace.co.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/colorplace_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Color%20Place%20%28K-pop%20Celeb%20Personal%20Color%29%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%AC%ED%94%8C%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4', true),
('color-signal-personal-color-makeup', 'Color Signal', '컬러시그널 (강남)', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangnam', '서울 강남구 강남역 인근', 'Personal color analysis', 'Thorough color analysis with interpreter service; reviewers note the team follows through even past closing time.', 'Reviewers praise both the thoroughness of the analysis and the interpreter service, and one account describes the team seeing things through diligently even after closing time. A 4.9 average across more than 900 reviews backs the pattern up.', 'visitors who want an interpreter on hand', 'Near Gangnam Station, Color Signal has built one of the larger review bases in this category — a 4.9 average across more than 900 ratings. Accounts describe a thorough analysis and single out the interpreter service, which removes the language barrier from what is essentially a long conversation about your own coloring. One review mentions a booking-time mix-up that the team resolved by working diligently past closing. Session information is on the official site, colorsignal.co.kr. If the interpreter matters to your visit, confirm that arrangement when you reserve.', 4.9, 909, 'https://colorsignal.co.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/color_signal_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Color%20Signal%20Personal%20Color%20%26%20Makeup%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%AC%EC%8B%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%84%90', true),
('colorize-personal-color-makeup-gangnam', 'Colorize (Gangnam)', '컬러라이즈 (강남)', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangnam', '서울 강남구 강남역 인근', 'Personal color analysis', 'Gangnam branch of the Colorize personal-color studio — same brand as the Myeongdong flagship.', null, 'the Colorize brand south of the river', 'This is the southern branch of Colorize, sharing its brand with the Myeongdong flagship but sitting near Gangnam Station instead — convenient if your itinerary keeps you below the river. The branch holds a 4.9 average across 320 reviews of its own. Details for both locations run through the shared website, colorize.co.kr, and the Instagram account @colorize_you. For most travelers the choice between the two studios comes down to geography; the flagship appears separately in this guide.', 4.9, 320, 'https://colorize.co.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/colorize_you', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Colorize%20Personal%20Color%20%26%20Makeup%20%28Gangnam%29%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%AC%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88', true),
('earthness-spa-aroma-massage', 'Earthness Spa', '어스니스 스파', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangnam', '서울 강남구', 'Aroma massage', 'Quiet aroma-oil massage studio in Gangnam.', null, 'a calm aroma-oil massage in Gangnam', 'A quiet aroma-oil massage studio in the Gangnam district, Earthness Spa is listed for a single specialty — aromatherapy massage — and holds a 4.9 rating from a small set of 19 reviews. Little else about the studio is published online, so it is worth confirming hours and availability before you go.', 4.9, 19, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Earthness%20Spa%20%28Aroma%20Massage%29%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%96%B4%EC%8A%A4%EB%8B%88%EC%8A%A4%20%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C', true),
('in-spa-premium-hotel-spa', 'IN SPA', '인스파 프리미엄 호텔스파', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangnam', '서울 강남구', 'Spa & massage', 'Premium hotel-style spa and massage in Gangnam.', null, 'a hotel-style spa session in Gangnam', 'In the Gangnam district, IN SPA offers spa and massage treatments in the premium hotel style its Korean name promises. It carries a 4.8 rating across 73 reviews. Details of the treatment menu are not widely published in English, so booking ahead — and confirming what each course includes — is a sensible first step.', 4.8, 73, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=IN%20SPA%20%28Premium%20Hotel%20Spa%29%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%9D%B8%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C%20%ED%94%84%EB%A6%AC%EB%AF%B8%EC%97%84%20%ED%98%B8%ED%85%94%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C', true),
('moclock-scalp-hair-loss-care', 'Moclock Scalp Care', '모클락 두피/탈모 케어', 'head_spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangnam', '서울 강남구', 'Scalp & hair-loss head spa', 'Scalp and hair-loss care specialist head spa in Gangnam.', null, 'targeted scalp and hair-loss concerns', 'Moclock is a head spa in Gangnam with a specific focus: scalp and hair-loss care. It holds a 4.4 rating across 32 reviews. Our records list only a district-level address and no website or Instagram, so confirm the exact location, hours, and prices through a map listing before making the trip.', 4.4, 32, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Moclock%20Scalp/Hair%20Loss%20Care%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%AA%A8%ED%81%B4%EB%9D%BD%20%EB%91%90%ED%94%BC/%ED%83%88%EB%AA%A8%20%EC%BC%80%EC%96%B4', true),
('myshopper-personal-color-shopping-guide', 'Myshopper', '마이쇼퍼', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangnam', '서울 강남구', 'Personal color & shopping guide', 'Personal color analysis paired with a guided shopping session.', null, 'turning a diagnosis into a shopping trip', 'Myshopper pairs a personal-color analysis with a guided shopping session in Gangnam, so the diagnosis carries directly into a shopping trip built around the results. The public record is modest — a 4.7 rating from 11 reviews, with no website or Instagram account listed — so treat the details as worth confirming through your booking channel before you commit to a time.', 4.7, 11, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Myshopper%20Personal%20Color%20%2B%20Shopping%20Guide%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%A7%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%87%BC%ED%8D%BC', true),
('cutloose-k-pop-hair-makeup', 'Cutloose', '컷루스', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Cheongdam', '서울 강남구 청담동 93-14, 1F', 'Hair & makeup', 'Cheongdam K-pop hair and makeup studio; the director''s creative styling made their Instagram the portfolio.', 'A perfect 5.0 across 34 reviews, and the director''s creative styling has made the studio''s Instagram its de facto portfolio — worth scrolling before you decide.', 'K-pop-inspired hair and makeup styling', 'Cutloose is a K-pop hair and makeup studio on the first floor at Cheongdam-dong 93-14. There is no website; the studio''s Instagram accounts — @cutloose_kr and the director''s own @cutloose_woo_, followed by about 62,000 people — function as both portfolio and point of contact. Reviews stand at a full 5.0 across 34 entries.

