('normalshop', 'Normalshop', '노멀샵', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Cheongdam', '서울 강남구 선릉로 753, 3-4층', 'Hair & makeup', 'Hair and makeup studio near Gangnam-gu Office Station — pets welcome.', 'Pets are welcome here, a considerate detail if you are traveling with a companion animal.', 'an appointment your pet can join', 'A hair and makeup studio on the third and fourth floors at Seolleung-ro 753, near Gangnam-gu Office Station in the Cheongdam area. The distinguishing note in our record is that pets may accompany their owners. No ratings or reviews are on file yet, so set expectations accordingly; the studio''s Instagram, @normalshop_official, is the place to confirm details before visiting.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/normalshop_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Normalshop%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%EA%B5%AC%EC%B2%AD/%EC%B2%AD%EB%8B%B4%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%85%B8%EB%A9%80%EC%83%B5', true),
('rolling-jay', 'Rolling Jay', '롤링제이', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Cheongdam', '서울 강남구 청담동 39-14', 'Hair & makeup', 'Hair and makeup salon between Cheongdam and Gangnam-gu Office Station.', null, 'hair and makeup in the Cheongdam area', 'Between Cheongdam-dong and Gangnam-gu Office Station, Rolling Jay handles both hair and makeup from its studio at Cheongdam-dong 39-14. There is no website; the salon posts at @rollingjay_official, while its makeup director runs @rollingjay_onymakeup with a following of about 75,000. No ratings or reviews appear in our record, so treat the Instagram feeds as your best preview and point of contact.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/rollingjay_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Rolling%20Jay%20%EA%B0%95%EB%82%A8%EA%B5%AC%EC%B2%AD/%EC%B2%AD%EB%8B%B4%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%A1%A4%EB%A7%81%EC%A0%9C%EC%9D%B4', true),
('juno-hair-gangseo-office', 'JUNO HAIR Gangseo', '준오헤어 (강서구)', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Gangseo', '서울 강서구', 'Hair salon', 'Gangseo branch of the JUNO HAIR chain.', null, 'a chain-standard cut in Gangseo', 'In the Gangseo district of Seoul, this JUNO HAIR branch offers the chain''s standard hair services. Our record lists no street address, rating, or reviews for this location, so check junohair.com or the main Instagram account, @junohair_official, to confirm the exact address and hours before making the trip.', null, null, 'https://junohair.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/junohair_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Juno%20Hair%20%28Gangseo%20Office%29%20%EA%B0%95%EC%84%9C%EA%B5%AC%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%A4%80%EC%98%A4%ED%97%A4%EC%96%B4', true),
