Reviews average 4.6 across 19 entries. For visitors, the practical route in is Creatrip, which handles bookings for the studio.', 4.6, 19, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/hosudosan_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=HOSU%20DOSAN%20%EB%8F%84%EC%82%B0/%EC%B2%AD%EB%8B%B4%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%ED%98%B8%EC%88%98%EB%8F%84%EC%82%B0', true),
('a3-nature-private-body-scrub', 'A3 Nature', 'A3 네이처 프라이빗 바디스크럽', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Dongdaemun', '서울 동대문', 'Body-scrub spa', 'Private Korean body-scrub spa in Dongdaemun.', null, 'a private Korean body-scrub session', 'A3 Nature is a private body-scrub spa in Dongdaemun, offering the Korean scrub in a private setting rather than a communal bathhouse. Public information about the shop is limited, so confirm hours and whether a reservation is required before visiting.', null, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=A3%20nature%20%28Private%20Body%20Scrub%29%20%EB%8F%99%EB%8C%80%EB%AC%B8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/A3%20%EB%84%A4%EC%9D%B4%EC%B2%98%20%ED%94%84%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B9%97%20%EB%B0%94%EB%94%94%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%9F%BD', true),
('sparex-sauna-good-morning-city-dongmyo', 'SPAREX Sauna', '스파렉스 (굿모닝시티/동묘점)', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Dongdaemun', '서울 동대문', 'Sauna & jjimjilbang', 'Classic jjimjilbang sauna in the Good Morning City building near Dongmyo.', null, 'an everyday Korean jjimjilbang experience', 'Inside the Good Morning City building near Dongmyo, in the Dongdaemun area, SPAREX is a classic Korean sauna and jjimjilbang — the communal bathhouse format rather than a private spa, and a fit for travelers curious about everyday Korean sauna culture. Published details are sparse, so check current hours before planning a visit around it.', null, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=SPAREX%20Sauna%20%28Good%20Morning%20City%20/%20Dongmyo%29%20%EB%8F%99%EB%8C%80%EB%AC%B8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C%EB%A0%89%EC%8A%A4', true),
('a-muu-hair-salon', 'A:MUU Hair Salon', '에이뮤헤어 (명동)', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동8나길 47, 3층', 'Hair salon', 'A 28-year veteran director — layered cuts, perms, and head spa, popular with visiting travelers.', 'The director brings 28 years of experience to layered cuts, perms, and head spa work, and the salon holds a 4.9 rating across 60 reviews.', 'layered cuts and perms from a veteran director', 'Three floors up at Myeongdong 8na-gil 47, A:MUU Hair Salon is led by a director with 28 years of experience, and the menu centers on layered cuts, perms, and head spa treatments. Foreign travelers make up a noticeable share of the clientele, according to reviews, and the salon holds a 4.9 rating across 60 of them.

The salon posts at @amuuhair_myeongdong, and the director keeps a personal account at @jyj8371; either works as a preview before you book.', 4.9, 60, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/amuuhair_myeongdong', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=A%3AMUU%20Hair%20Salon%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%97%90%EC%9D%B4%EB%AE%A4%ED%97%A4%EC%96%B4', true),
('anskin-myeongdong', 'ANSKIN', '안스킨 명동', 'facial'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Facial care', 'Facial care studio in the heart of Myeongdong.', null, 'a straightforward facial in central Myeongdong', 'ANSKIN is a facial-care studio in the heart of Myeongdong. The listing is brief — no website or Instagram is on record — but its rating stands at a full 5.0 across 29 reviews. With so few online details available, confirm opening hours and availability locally before planning your day around a visit.', 5, 29, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=ANSKIN%20Myeongdong%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%95%88%EC%8A%A4%ED%82%A8%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99', true),
('art-de-la-peau', 'Art de la Peau', '아르드라뽀 (명동)', 'facial'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Esthetic facials & massage', 'Esthetic facials and massage — one of Myeongdong''s best-reviewed skincare rooms.', 'A 4.9 average across 487 reviews is a rare depth of feedback for a neighborhood skincare room, and it backs the studio''s standing as one of Myeongdong''s best-reviewed.', 'well-reviewed esthetic facials in Myeongdong', 'Few Myeongdong skincare rooms carry a track record like this one. Art de la Peau pairs esthetic facials with massage, and its 4.9 average across 487 reviews makes it one of the district''s best-reviewed places for skin care. The studio sits in central Myeongdong, within Seoul''s Jung-gu. No website or Instagram is listed in our record, so plan to confirm booking details on the ground.', 4.9, 487, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Art%20de%20la%20peau%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%95%84%EB%A5%B4%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EB%BD%80', true),
('cocorea-makeup-hair', 'Cocorea', '코코레아 (명동)', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동4길 21, 1F', 'Personal color, hair & makeup', 'Personal color plus hair and makeup in one sitting; bookings run through Klook and Naver.', 'Folding hair and makeup into the same appointment as the diagnosis is a practical format for travelers on a schedule.', 'diagnosis and a makeover in one sitting', 'Cocorea''s premise is efficiency: a personal-color diagnosis followed by hair and makeup in the same sitting, at a first-floor studio on Myeongdong 4-gil. It holds a 4.6 rating from 146 reviews. There is no official website — reservations run through Klook and Naver instead — and the studio''s Instagram account is @cocoreamakeup. The format has a clear logic for visitors: rather than taking your results home as theory, you walk out already styled to the palette you were just given.', 4.6, 146, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/cocoreamakeup', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Cocorea%20Makeup%20%26%20Hair%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%BD%94%EC%BD%94%EB%A0%88%EC%95%84', true),
('colorize-personal-color-analysis-makeup', 'Colorize (Myeongdong)', '컬러라이즈 (명동)', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 퇴계로 145, 1F', 'Personal color analysis & makeup', 'The Colorize flagship — consultants explain why each color works, down to shopping picks. 2,400+ reviews.', 'The numbers are striking — 2,400-plus reviews at 4.9 — but the substance is the explanation: clients leave understanding why their palette works, with shopping picks to act on it.', 'understanding the reasoning behind your palette', 'With more than 2,400 reviews holding a 4.9 average, the Colorize flagship on Toegye-ro is among the most-reviewed studios in this category. What clients single out is the teaching: consultants such as Dana and Lucy explain why a particular color works on you rather than simply naming your season, and the session carries through to concrete shopping recommendations. Makeup is offered alongside the diagnosis. Details are on the official site, colorize.co.kr, and the same brand operates a second branch near Gangnam Station if the south side of the city suits your plans better.', 4.9, 2417, 'https://colorize.co.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/colorize_you', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Colorize%20Personal%20Color%20Analysis%20%26%20Makeup%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%AC%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88', true),
('hana-mud-spa', 'Hana Mud Spa', '하나머드스파 (명동)', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동8길 21-5, 5층', 'Women-only mud spa', 'Women-only mud sauna and massage with Korean-style amethyst sauna rooms; book via Creatrip or Klook.', 'A women-only format with mud and amethyst sauna rooms is a distinctive combination, and booking through Creatrip or Klook keeps reservations simple for visitors.', 'women seeking a mud-sauna session', 'Hana Mud Spa is a women-only spa on the fifth floor of a building on Myeongdong 8-gil, combining a mud sauna, Korean-style and amethyst sauna rooms, and massage. It holds a 4.5 rating across 62 reviews. Reservations run through Creatrip or Klook, which makes booking straightforward for English-speaking visitors; note the women-only policy before planning a visit in mixed company.', 4.5, 62, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hana%20Mud%20Spa%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%ED%95%98%EB%82%98%EB%A8%B8%EB%93%9C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C', true),
('herique-hair', 'Herique Hair', '에리크 (명동)', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동10길 18, 5F', 'Hair salon', 'Well-reviewed Myeongdong hair salon with 460+ ratings.', 'A 4.6 average across more than 460 ratings is a substantial sample for a single salon, which lends the score real weight.', 'a well-reviewed haircut in Myeongdong', 'Herique Hair occupies a fifth-floor space at Myeongdong 10-gil 18. It is one of the most-reviewed hair salons in our Myeongdong records, with a 4.6 average across more than 460 ratings. Beyond haircuts, the record lists no further service detail, so consult the salon''s Instagram, @herique.official, for current work and to make contact — no website or booking platform is listed.', 4.6, 460, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/herique.official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Herique%20Hair%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%97%90%EB%A6%AC%ED%81%AC', true),
('juno-hair-myeongdong-street', 'JUNO HAIR Myeongdong', '준오헤어 명동스트리트점', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동 (지점 다수)', 'Hair & head spa', 'Myeongdong Street branch of the JUNO HAIR chain — hair and head spa.', 'A 4.6 rating across 154 reviews suggests the big-chain consistency holds at this branch, and the head spa menu adds a reason to stay beyond the cut.', 'pairing a haircut with a head spa', 'The Myeongdong Street location is one of several JUNO HAIR branches in the neighborhood — the chain operates many outposts across Seoul, each with its own Instagram account alongside the head-office @junohair_official. This branch offers hair services and head spa treatments and carries a 4.6 rating across 154 reviews.

The branch account is @juno_myeongdong2, and junohair.com covers the chain as a whole. With multiple Myeongdong locations, confirm which branch you have booked before you set out.', 4.6, 154, 'https://junohair.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/junohair_official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=JUNO%20HAIR%20Myeongdong%20Street%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%A4%80%EC%98%A4%ED%97%A4%EC%96%B4%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EB%A6%AC%ED%8A%B8%EC%A0%90', true),
('line-esthe-facial-care', 'Line Esthe', '라인에스테 페이셜케어', 'facial'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Facial treatments', 'Facial-care room in Myeongdong with consistently high ratings.', 'Consistency is the draw here: a 4.9 average across 158 reviews suggests the experience holds up visit after visit.', 'a consistently well-rated Myeongdong facial', 'In central Myeongdong, Line Esthe keeps its focus squarely on facial care, and its ratings have stayed consistently high — a 4.9 average across 158 reviews at last count. That consistency is the main reason it appears here. Our record lists no website or Instagram, so confirm hours and availability locally rather than relying on online booking.', 4.9, 158, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Line%20Esthe%20Facial%20Care%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8%EC%97%90%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%8C%20%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%9C%EC%BC%80%EC%96%B4', true),
('mizo-massage-rooftop-spa', 'MIZO Rooftop Spa', '미조 마사지 루프탑 스파', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Full-body, foot & facial spa', 'Rooftop spa combining full-body, foot, and facial care.', null, 'covering body, foot, and face in one visit', 'MIZO combines full-body, foot, and facial treatments at a rooftop spa in Myeongdong, so a single booking can cover all three. It rates 4.7 across 95 reviews, and the location is easy to fold into a Myeongdong afternoon. Details beyond that are limited, so confirm course options and timing when booking.', 4.7, 95, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=MIZO%20Massage%20Rooftop%20Spa%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%AF%B8%EC%A1%B0%20%EB%A7%88%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%80%20%EB%A3%A8%ED%94%84%ED%83%91%20%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C', true),
('myeongdong-beauty-skyview-spa', 'Myeongdong Beauty Skyview Spa', '명동뷰티 스카이뷰 스파', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동 (명동역 도보 1분)', 'Full-body & facial spa', 'Hot stone, full-body massage, and facial with a rooftop view, one minute from Myeongdong Station.', 'A 4.9 rating across 435 reviews is hard to argue with, and reviewers consistently mention well-judged pressure and friendly staff rather than only the view.', 'a massage with a rooftop view', 'One minute on foot from Myeongdong Station, this spa pairs a hot-stone and full-body massage with a facial, taken in with a rooftop view. It holds a 4.9 rating across 435 reviews, and Korean reviews repeatedly note moderate, well-judged pressure and friendly staff. Find it on Instagram at @mdbty77; the station-adjacent location makes it easy to slot in at the end of a day in the neighborhood.', 4.9, 435, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/mdbty77', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Myeongdong%20Beauty%20Skyview%20Spa%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%EB%B7%B0%ED%8B%B0%20%EC%8A%A4%EC%B9%B4%EC%9D%B4%EB%B7%B0%20%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C', true),
('myeongdong-condition-body-head-massage', 'Myeongdong Condition', '명동 컨디션 전신&헤드마사지', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Body & head massage', 'Body and head massage studio in Myeongdong.', null, 'easing body and head tension', 'Myeongdong Condition is a massage studio in Myeongdong focused on full-body and head massage. It carries a 4.8 rating from 227 reviews, and the head-massage option is the reason to pick it when head and scalp tension are the main complaint. Beyond the rating, published details are thin, so confirm hours and courses directly before visiting.', 4.8, 227, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Myeongdong%20Condition%20%28Body%20%26%20Head%20Massage%29%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20%EC%BB%A8%EB%94%94%EC%85%98%20%EC%A0%84%EC%8B%A0%26%ED%97%A4%EB%93%9C%EB%A7%88%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%80', true),
('myeongdong-skinspa', 'Myeongdong Skinspa', '스킨스파명동본점', 'facial'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Facials & skincare', 'Korean-style facials, RF lifting, and skin boosters at the Skinspa flagship.', 'The menu reaches past the standard facial — Korean-style facial care sits alongside RF (radio-frequency) lifting and a range of skin boosters at the brand''s flagship.', 'facials plus RF lifting and skin boosters', 'The flagship of the Skinspa brand sits in Myeongdong and covers more than a basic facial menu: Korean-style facial care, RF (radio-frequency) lifting, and a range of skin boosters. Our record carries no rating data for this branch, so the most current picture comes from its Instagram, @skinspa_korea, which has around 4,400 followers. If you are considering a device-based treatment such as RF lifting, it is worth messaging ahead to check what is available.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/skinspa_korea', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Myeongdong%20Skinspa%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%8A%A4%ED%82%A8%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%EB%B3%B8%EC%A0%90', true),
('o-hui-whoo-spa-massage', 'O HUI & WHOO Spa', '오휘&후 스파&마사지', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Spa & massage', 'Spa and massage built around the O HUI and WHOO cosmetic lines — 1,000+ reviews.', 'More than a thousand reviews at a 4.6 average is unusual volume, and treatments built on named cosmetic lines make it easy to know what is being used on your skin.', 'fans of O HUI and WHOO products', 'This Myeongdong spa builds its treatments around the O HUI and WHOO Korean cosmetic lines and has accumulated more than 1,000 reviews — 1,007 at a 4.6 average at last count. For visitors already loyal to either brand, being treated with the products themselves is the draw. Given that volume of reviews, booking ahead is advisable.', 4.6, 1007, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=O%20HUI%20%26%20WHOO%20Spa%20%26%20Massage%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%98%A4%ED%9C%98%26%ED%9B%84%20%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C%26%EB%A7%88%EC%82%AC%EC%A7%80', true),
('parkjun-beautylab', 'Parkjun BeautyLab', '박준뷰티랩 (명동/강남/청담)', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '명동8길 27 솔라리아호텔 5F / 강남 신논현역 5번 출구 도보 5분', 'Hair, head spa & makeup', 'Total beauty lab known for its signature 15-step scalp treatment; a favorite among visiting travelers.', 'Foreign visitors know the brand for its signature 15-step scalp treatment, and the operation runs largely on Instagram; on Klook, the Seongsu branch holds a 5.0, albeit from just nine reviews.', 'a signature 15-step scalp treatment', 'Parkjun BeautyLab is a total-beauty operation spanning hair, head spa, and makeup, with locations including a Myeongdong studio on the fifth floor of the Solaria Hotel at Myeongdong 8-gil 27 and a Gangnam branch about five minutes on foot from Sinnonhyeon Station exit 5. Among visiting travelers the brand is best known for its signature 15-step scalp treatment.

The Myeongdong and Gangnam branches run their own Instagram accounts — @parkjunbeautylab and @parkjunbeautylab_gangnam — alongside the head-office account. The Seongsu branch is listed on Klook, where it holds a 5.0 from nine reviews.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/parkjunbeautylab', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Parkjun%20BeautyLab%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%B0%95%EC%A4%80%EB%B7%B0%ED%8B%B0%EB%9E%A9', true),
('spa-1978-red-ginseng-ritual', 'SPA 1978', '스파 1978 (구 1899) 홍삼 리츄얼', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동', 'Spa', 'Red-ginseng ritual spa (formerly SPA 1899) in Myeongdong.', 'The red-ginseng ritual gives the visit a clearly Korean identity, and a 4.7 average over 341 reviews suggests the concept is more than branding.', 'a distinctly Korean red-ginseng ritual', 'SPA 1978, which previously operated as SPA 1899, anchors its Myeongdong treatments in a red-ginseng ritual. It rates 4.7 across 341 reviews. If you want a treatment that feels specifically Korean rather than generically relaxing, the ginseng focus is the reason to choose it; course details are best confirmed when booking.', 4.7, 341, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=SPA%201978%20Red%20Ginseng%20Ritual%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C%201978', true),
('the-bom-personal-color-makeup', 'The Bom', '더봄 (명동)', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 퇴계로18길 7', 'Personal color analysis', 'Personal color and makeup studio on Toegye-ro, near Myeongdong.', null, 'a straightforward analysis near Myeongdong', 'The Bom is a personal color and makeup studio on Toegye-ro 18-gil, within easy reach of central Myeongdong, and holds a 4.8 rating across 179 reviews. Its website, thebom.day, and Instagram account, @studio_thebom_, are the places to check session formats and current availability. Beyond the strong rating, little detail is on public record, so confirm specifics directly if your schedule depends on them.', 4.8, 179, 'https://thebom.day', 'https://www.instagram.com/studio_thebom_', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=The%20Bom%20Personal%20Color%20%26%20Makeup%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%8D%94%EB%B4%84', true),
('ye-lead-hair-styling', 'Ye_Lead Hair', '예리드 (명동)', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Myeongdong', '서울 중구 명동8가길 26, 3층', 'Hair', 'Premium salon built around an 18-step signature scalp treatment.', 'The salon has built its identity around an 18-step signature scalp treatment, and a 4.8 rating across 123 reviews suggests the ritual holds up.', 'an 18-step signature scalp treatment', 'On the third floor at Myeongdong 8ga-gil 26, Ye_Lead positions itself as a premium hair salon whose centerpiece is an 18-step signature scalp treatment. The salon holds a 4.8 rating from 123 reviews, and its Instagram account, @ye_lead, is the most direct window into current work. There is no official website listed, so checking Instagram before you go is the practical first step.', 4.8, 123, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/ye_lead', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ye_Lead%20Hair%20Styling%20%EB%AA%85%EB%8F%99%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%98%88%EB%A6%AC%EB%93%9C', true),
('argyol-seongsu', 'Argyol', '아르결 (성수)', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '명동/강남/홍대/성수 4개 지점', 'K-beauty styling & head spa', 'K-beauty styling bar with a 15-step head spa; four branches across Seoul.', 'A 15-step head spa is an unusually thorough menu item for a styling bar, and the brand runs four branches across Seoul.', 'pairing a styling session with a head spa', 'Argyol runs four branches across Seoul — Myeongdong, Gangnam, Hongdae, and this one in Seongsu — under a K-beauty styling concept anchored by a 15-step head spa. Several branches keep their own Instagram accounts (@a.rgyol_seongsu for the Seongsu location), so the branch page is the most direct place to check current work. No ratings or review counts are published for this location, so confirm details through the branch account before booking.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/a.rgyol_seongsu', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Argyol%20%28Seongsu%29%20%EC%84%B1%EC%88%98%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%95%84%EB%A5%B4%EA%B2%B0', true),
('jungsaemmool-k-beauty-makeup-class-seongsu-101', 'JUNGSAEMMOOL Makeup Class', '정샘물 K-뷰티 메이크업 클래스 (성수)', 'makeup'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수동 (성수 101)', 'Makeup class', 'JUNGSAEMMOOL''s group makeup class with 1:1 touches — take home a fan-size product and use the photo booth after.', 'The format blends a group class with one-on-one touches, so you get something close to a private tutorial without the private price. A fan-size product to take home and a photo booth at the end are thoughtful extras.', 'a group K-beauty makeup class with 1:1 touches', 'In Seongsu, the JUNGSAEMMOOL brand runs its K-beauty makeup class out of the Seongsu 101 space in Seongdong-gu. The session pairs a group format with one-on-one touches, which reviewers say delivers much of the effect of a private tutorial at a group-class price. At the end, each participant takes home a fan-size product and can step into the on-site photo booth.

The class holds a 4.7 rating across 141 reviews. There is no website listed, so the Instagram accounts @jsmbeauty_101_seongsu and @jungsaemmool11 are the place to look for current details.', 4.7, 141, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/jsmbeauty_101_seongsu', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=JUNGSAEMMOOL%20K-Beauty%20Makeup%20Class%20%28Seongsu%20101%29%20%EC%84%B1%EC%88%98%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%A0%95%EC%83%98%EB%AC%BC%20K-%EB%B7%B0%ED%8B%B0%20%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B4%ED%81%AC%EC%97%85%20%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4', true),
('mercdi-hair-salon', 'Mércdi Hair Salon', '메르크디 (성수)', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수동', 'Hair', 'Small Seongsu hair salon; official web presence and exact location unverified.', null, 'a haircut in Seongsu, once confirmed', 'Mércdi is a small hair salon in Seongsu-dong that currently holds a 5.0 rating from a dozen reviews. Its public footprint is thin: the Instagram account (@mercdi_) is limited, no official website has been confirmed, and the exact address is also unverified — searches tend to surface an unrelated fashion brand with a similar name instead. Until those details are checked, confirm the location directly before making the trip.', 5, 12, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/mercdi_', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=M%C3%A9rcdi%20Hair%20Salon%20%EC%84%B1%EC%88%98%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%A9%94%EB%A5%B4%ED%81%AC%EB%94%94', false),
('whipped-face-mask-cleanser-class', 'WHIPPED', '휩드 (성수)', 'facial'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수이로20길 16', 'DIY beauty class', 'One-day vegan class in Seongsu — whip up your own cleanser and face mask.', 'Whipping your own vegan cleanser and face mask is a different kind of beauty outing in Seongsu, and a 4.9 average across 37 reviews suggests the class delivers.', 'making your own vegan cleanser and mask', 'Over in Seongsu, WHIPPED runs a one-day vegan beauty class where you make your own cleanser and face mask rather than buying one. It is an experience rather than a treatment — you leave with something you whipped up yourself. The studio sits at 16 Seongsui-ro 20-gil in Seongdong-gu, and its rating stands at 4.9 across 37 reviews. Class schedules and sign-up details are best checked through its Instagram, @whipped._official, which counts roughly 75,000 followers.', 4.9, 37, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/whipped._official', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=WHIPPED%20%28Face%20Mask%20%26%20Cleanser%20Class%29%20%EC%84%B1%EC%88%98%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%ED%9C%A9%EB%93%9C', true),
('the-foret-spa-seoul-forest', 'THE FORET SPA', '더포레스파 서울숲역점', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 서울숲역 인근', 'Spa', 'Private-room premium spa near Seoul Forest Station; head spa and anti-aging care draw high marks.', 'Korean reviewers consistently praise the quiet, private-room setting, with the head-spa and anti-aging treatments drawing the highest marks.', 'a quiet private-room head spa', 'Near Seoul Forest Station in Seongsu, THE FORET SPA runs a premium private-room format with a notably quiet atmosphere, and its head-spa and anti-aging care draw particular satisfaction in Korean reviews. It rates 4.9 across 77 reviews. Menu and booking details are on its website, theforetspa.co.kr, with updates on Instagram at @theforet_spa — both worth checking before you plan a visit.', 4.9, 77, 'https://theforetspa.co.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/theforet_spa', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=THE%20FORET%20SPA%20%28Seoul%20Forest%29%20%EC%84%B1%EC%88%98/%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%EC%88%B2%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%8D%94%ED%8F%AC%EB%A0%88%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%8C%20%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%EC%88%B2%EC%97%AD%EC%A0%90', true),
