('arz-make-up-cheongdam', 'ARZ MAKE UP', '아르즈청담', 'makeup'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Cheongdam', '서울 강남구 청담동 2-10, 6F', 'Wedding & photoshoot hair and makeup', 'Cheongdam studio specialized in wedding and photoshoot makeup.', 'The studio is devoted specifically to wedding and photoshoot hair and makeup, and its 15 reviews average a straight 5.0.', 'wedding and photoshoot makeup in Cheongdam', 'On the sixth floor at 2-10 Cheongdam-dong in Gangnam, ARZ MAKE UP is a hair and makeup studio that concentrates on wedding and photoshoot work. Its review record is brief but strong: a 5.0 rating from 15 reviews.

There is no website, so the Instagram accounts — the studio''s @arz_cheongdam and the CEO''s @arz_mika — are the practical channels for inquiries. Given the narrow specialization, this is the address to note if wedding or photoshoot makeup is what brings you to Seoul.', 5, 15, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/arz_cheongdam', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=ARZ%20MAKE%20UP%20Cheongdam%20%EC%B2%AD%EB%8B%B4%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%95%84%EB%A5%B4%EC%A6%88%EC%B2%AD%EB%8B%B4', true),
