('color-of-you-personal-color-analysis', 'Color of You', '컬러오브유 (홍대)', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Hongdae', '서울 마포구 동교로 209, 3F', 'Personal color analysis', 'Popular with travelers — seasonal tone analysis you can apply right away, in English.', 'The praise is specific — English-language sessions whose seasonal verdicts travelers can put to use the same day — and a 5.0 average across 216 reviews backs it up.', 'English-language analysis you can use immediately', 'Travelers account for much of the following at Color of You, a third-floor studio on Donggyo-ro in Hongdae with a 5.0 rating across 216 reviews. Sessions run in English, and reviewers note that the seasonal diagnosis — learning you are a Summer, for instance — arrives with guidance concrete enough to apply the same day rather than file away. There is no website; the Instagram account @color_of_you_ is the studio''s public point of reference for current details.', 5, 216, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/color_of_you_', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Color%20of%20You%20Personal%20Color%20Analysis%20%ED%99%8D%EB%8C%80%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%BB%AC%EB%9F%AC%EC%98%A4%EB%B8%8C%EC%9C%A0', true),
('damda-private-korean-bath-body-scrub', 'DAMDA', '담다 (홍대)', 'spa'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Hongdae', '서울 마포구 홍대', 'Bath & body-scrub spa', 'Private Korean bath, body scrub, and hair care in one course — a gentle first-seshin experience.', 'A 5.0 average across 127 reviews is remarkable, and Korean reviewers repeatedly recommend the private bath-scrub-hair course as a gentle way into a first seshin.', 'a first Korean body-scrub experience', 'In Hongdae, DAMDA folds a private Korean bath, a seshin body scrub, and hair care into a single course — a gentler introduction to the scrub tradition than a communal bathhouse. It holds a perfect 5.0 across 127 reviews, the course is especially popular with women, and Korean reviews often recommend it to first-time seshin visitors. Details are on its website and on Instagram at @seshinshop_damda.', 5, 127, 'https://seshinshopdamda.my.canva.site', 'https://www.instagram.com/seshinshop_damda', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=DAMDA%20Private%20Korean%20Bath%20%26%20Body%20Scrub%20%ED%99%8D%EB%8C%80%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%8B%B4%EB%8B%A4', true),
('forena-clinic', 'Forena Clinic', '포레나클리닉 (홍대)', 'clinic'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Hongdae', '서울 마포구 양화로 140, 7층 (홍대역 9번 출구 도보 1분)', 'Dermatology clinic', 'Foreigner-friendly dermatology clinic a minute from Hongik Univ. Station — Ulthera, Thermage, Rejuran.', 'A separate global Instagram account, @forenaclinic_global, runs alongside the main channel of roughly 36,000 followers, and the one-minute walk from Hongik University Station keeps a first visit simple.', 'foreigner-friendly Ulthera, Thermage, and Rejuran', 'One minute on foot from Exit 9 of Hongik University Station, Forena Clinic occupies the seventh floor of 140 Yanghwa-ro in Hongdae. The clinic describes itself as foreigner-friendly and offers treatments including Ulthera, Thermage, and Rejuran.

Alongside its main Instagram account, @forenaclinic, with around 36,000 followers, Forena maintains a separate global account, @forenaclinic_global; further details are available through its website, forenaclinic.com. No visitor ratings are on record yet, so reviewing those channels before booking is worthwhile.', null, null, 'https://forenaclinic.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/forenaclinic', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Forena%20Clinic%20%ED%99%8D%EB%8C%80%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%ED%8F%AC%EB%A0%88%EB%82%98%ED%81%B4%EB%A6%AC%EB%8B%89', true),
