('kimchi-making-class-with-chef-hakyung-at-gyeongbokgung', 'Kimchi Class with Chef Hakyung', '경복궁 하경 셰프 김치 클래스', 'cooking_class'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Bukchon', '서울 종로구 경복궁 인근', 'Kimchi-making class', 'Kimchi-making class with Chef Hakyung near Gyeongbokgung.', null, 'a kimchi lesson near Gyeongbokgung', 'Led by Chef Hakyung, this kimchi-making class takes place near Gyeongbokgung Palace in Jongno-gu, in the Bukchon area. The session is devoted entirely to kimchi, and the location is simple to pair with a morning at the palace or a walk through Bukchon afterward.', 5, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kimchi%20Making%20Class%20with%20Chef%20Hakyung%20at%20Gyeongbokgung%20%EA%B2%BD%EB%B3%B5%EA%B6%81%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EA%B2%BD%EB%B3%B5%EA%B6%81%20%ED%95%98%EA%B2%BD%20%EC%85%B0%ED%94%84%20%EA%B9%80%EC%B9%98%20%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4', true),
('cooking-class-in-mangwon-market-with-michelin-starred-chef', 'Mangwon Market Chef''s Cooking Class', '망원시장 미슐랭 셰프 쿠킹클래스 (Chef Pano)', 'cooking_class'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Mangwon', '서울 마포구 망원시장', 'Market & Michelin-chef cooking class', 'Shop Mangwon Market with a Michelin-experienced chef, then cook what you found — closer to cultural exchange than a lesson.', 'Reviewers describe it as closer to cultural exchange than a lesson — shopping Mangwon Market with Chef Pano before cooking together — and the clean, spacious studio draws its own praise.', 'market-to-table cooking with a professional chef', 'At Mangwon Market in Mapo-gu, Chef Pano — a chef with Michelin restaurant experience — begins the class with a walk through the market stalls, shopping for the day''s ingredients before heading back to cook them together. Reviewers describe the format as closer to a cultural exchange than a formal lesson, and note that the studio is clean and spacious.

The class holds a 5.0 rating across 28 reviews; updates are posted on Instagram at @seoulfoodventure and @seoulcookingclub.', 5, 28, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/seoulfoodventure', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Cooking%20Class%20in%20Mangwon%20Market%20with%20Michelin-Starred%20Chef%20%EB%A7%88%ED%8F%AC/%EB%A7%9D%EC%9B%90%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%A7%9D%EC%9B%90%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20%EB%AF%B8%EC%8A%90%EB%9E%AD%20%EC%85%B0%ED%94%84%20%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%B9%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4', true),
('korean-cooking-class-with-grocery-shopping-at-seoul-local-market', 'Market-to-Table Cooking Class', '서울 로컬시장 장보기 한식 쿠킹클래스', 'cooking_class'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Mangwon', '서울 마포구 망원시장', 'Market grocery-shopping cooking class', 'Korean cooking class that starts with grocery shopping in Mangwon Market.', null, 'shopping and cooking like a local', 'The session begins not at a stove but in the aisles of Mangwon Market in Mapo-gu, where participants shop for groceries before cooking a Korean meal with what they found. It is a straightforward market-to-table format; plan for the shopping portion as part of the class time rather than a separate activity.', 5, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Korean%20Cooking%20Class%20with%20Grocery%20Shopping%20at%20Seoul%20Local%20Market%20%EB%A7%88%ED%8F%AC/%EB%A7%9D%EC%9B%90%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%20%EB%A1%9C%EC%BB%AC%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20%EC%9E%A5%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0%20%ED%95%9C%EC%8B%9D%20%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%B9%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4', true),
('kimchi-cooking-class-in-traditional-hanok-house', 'Hanok Kimchi Cooking Class', '전통 한옥 김치 쿠킹클래스', 'cooking_class'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Bukchon', '서울 종로구 북촌/경복궁 인근', 'Kimchi cooking class', 'Kimchi class held in a traditional hanok near Bukchon.', null, 'making kimchi inside a traditional hanok', 'Held in a traditional hanok house in Jongno-gu, near Bukchon and Gyeongbokgung, this class is devoted to a single subject: kimchi. The hanok venue is the distinguishing detail, and the location keeps the palace and the rest of Bukchon close at hand.', 5, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kimchi%20Cooking%20Class%20in%20Traditional%20Hanok%20House%20%EB%B6%81%EC%B4%8C/%EA%B2%BD%EB%B3%B5%EA%B6%81%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%A0%84%ED%86%B5%20%ED%95%9C%EC%98%A5%20%EA%B9%80%EC%B9%98%20%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%B9%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4', true),
('royal-seoul-cooking-class-in-a-100-year-old-hanok', 'Royal Seoul Cooking Class', '100년 한옥 로열 서울 쿠킹클래스', 'cooking_class'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Bukchon', '서울 종로구 북촌/경복궁 인근', 'Hanok & market cooking class', 'Royal Korean cooking in a 100-year-old hanok, paired with a market tour.', 'Ninety-eight reviewers rate it 5.0, with particular praise for the instructors'' background knowledge and considerate pacing.', 'royal recipes and a market tour', 'A century-old hanok in the Bukchon area is the setting for this class, which pairs royal-style Korean cooking with a tour of a local market. Reviewers praise the instructors — Park is mentioned by name — for their depth of background knowledge and considerate pacing.

It holds a 5.0 rating across 98 reviews, and the hanok sits near Gyeongbokgung in Jongno-gu, so it combines easily with a palace visit. Updates are posted at @royalseoulcc on Instagram.', 5, 98, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/royalseoulcc', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Royal%20Seoul%20Cooking%20Class%20in%20a%20100-Year-Old%20Hanok%20%EB%B6%81%EC%B4%8C/%EA%B2%BD%EB%B3%B5%EA%B6%81%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/100%EB%85%84%20%ED%95%9C%EC%98%A5%20%EB%A1%9C%EC%97%B4%20%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%20%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%B9%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4', true),
('traditional-korean-6-dish-cooking-class-hidden-alley-tour', 'Korean 6-Dish Class & Alley Tour', '전통 한식 6첩 쿠킹클래스 + 히든 골목투어', 'cooking_class'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Bukchon', '서울 종로구 북촌/경복궁 인근', 'Six-dish cooking class & alley tour', 'Six-dish traditional Korean cooking class plus a hidden-alley walking tour.', null, 'a full Korean table plus neighborhood walk', 'Six traditional Korean dishes are on the menu here, cooked in a single session before the group heads out for a walking tour of alleys near Bukchon and Gyeongbokgung in Jongno-gu. Because the class and the tour come as one combined program, plan your schedule around both parts rather than the cooking alone.', 5, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Traditional%20Korean%206-Dish%20Cooking%20Class%20%2B%20Hidden%20Alley%20Tour%20%EB%B6%81%EC%B4%8C/%EA%B2%BD%EB%B3%B5%EA%B6%81%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%A0%84%ED%86%B5%20%ED%95%9C%EC%8B%9D%206%EC%B2%A9%20%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%B9%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%20%2B%20%ED%9E%88%EB%93%A0%20%EA%B3%A8%EB%AA%A9%ED%88%AC%EC%96%B4', true),
('seoul-soju-makgeolli-tasting-experience', 'Soju & Makgeolli Tasting', '서울 소주·막걸리 테이스팅', 'food_tour'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, null, '서울 (증류소 등)', 'Traditional Korean liquor tasting', 'Soju and makgeolli tastings, from distillery visits to guided flights.', null, 'a guided introduction to soju and makgeolli', 'These tastings introduce Korea''s traditional alcohols — soju and makgeolli — in formats that range from guided flights to distillery visits in Seoul. Session titles such as "Seoul Soju Tasting at Distillery" and "Discover Traditional Soju & Makgeolli" give a sense of the spread on offer.

Because the formats differ, it is worth confirming whether your session is a seated tasting or a distillery visit before you book.', null, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Seoul%20Soju%20%26%20Makgeolli%20Tasting%20Experience%20%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%20%EC%86%8C%EC%A3%BC%C2%B7%EB%A7%89%EA%B1%B8%EB%A6%AC%20%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%85', true),
('where-locals-eat-korean-bbq-dry-aged-hanwoo', 'Where Locals Eat: Korean BBQ', '로컬 한식 BBQ / 드라이에이징 한우 체험', 'food_tour'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, null, '지역 비공개', 'Hanwoo & Korean BBQ experience', 'Hosted Korean BBQ and dry-aged hanwoo dinners where locals actually eat.', null, 'diners curious about dry-aged hanwoo beef', 'Hosted dinners built around Korean BBQ and dry-aged hanwoo beef, held at the kind of restaurants where locals actually eat. Formats vary — listings such as "Korean BBQ of the Month," "Private Korean BBQ with Jason," and "A Gourmet Korean BBQ & Dry-Aged Hanwoo" suggest both private and gourmet-dinner versions of the experience.

One practical note: the venue''s location is not publicly disclosed, so plan around receiving the specifics through the booking rather than mapping it out in advance.', null, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Where%20Locals%20Eat%3A%20Korean%20BBQ%20/%20Dry-Aged%20Hanwoo%20%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%28%EB%B9%84%EA%B3%B5%EA%B0%9C%29%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%A1%9C%EC%BB%AC%20%ED%95%9C%EC%8B%9D%20BBQ%20/%20%EB%93%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EC%97%90%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%95%20%ED%95%9C%EC%9A%B0%20%EC%B2%B4%ED%97%98', true),
('brewing-makgeolli-experience', 'Makgeolli Brewing Experience', '막걸리 만들기 체험 (성수)', 'cooking_class'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수동', 'Traditional makgeolli brewing workshop', 'Brew your own makgeolli in a Seongsu workshop.', null, 'brewing your own Korean rice wine', 'Over in Seongsu-dong, Seongdong-gu, this workshop centers on brewing makgeolli, Korea''s traditional rice wine, and each participant makes their own batch. As a traditional-liquor workshop rather than a cooking class in the usual sense, it suits visitors who have already tried a kimchi or banchan class and want to go one step further.', 5, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Brewing%20Makgeolli%20Experience%20%EC%84%B1%EC%88%98%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%A7%89%EA%B1%B8%EB%A6%AC%20%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0%20%EC%B2%B4%ED%97%98', true),
('the-seoul-pub-crawl', 'The Seoul Pub Crawl', '더 서울 펍크롤', 'food_tour'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Itaewon', '서울 용산구 이태원 기반', 'Nightlife pub crawl', 'Itaewon-based pub crawl through Seoul''s nightlife.', null, 'a sociable evening out in Itaewon', 'Based in Itaewon, in Yongsan-gu, this pub crawl moves a group through Seoul''s nightlife over the course of an evening and currently holds a 4.7 rating. Published details beyond the Itaewon base are limited, so check the current schedule and meeting point when booking — and expect a late-night, social format rather than a quiet tasting.', 4.7, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=The%20Seoul%20Pub%20Crawl%20%EC%9D%B4%ED%83%9C%EC%9B%90%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EB%8D%94%20%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%20%ED%8E%8D%ED%81%AC%EB%A1%A4', true),
('gwangjang-market-half-day-street-food-experience', 'Gwangjang Street Food Tour', '광장시장 반나절 스트리트푸드 투어(+기념품)', 'food_tour'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Jongno', '서울 종로구 광장시장', 'Street-food market tour', 'Half-day Gwangjang Market street-food tour run like a stamp-rally challenge — guides get repeat praise.', 'Reviewers keep returning to the guides — Cecilia''s local knowledge and friendliness come up again and again — and the tour holds a 4.9 rating across 179 reviews.', 'a first guided taste of Gwangjang Market', 'A half-day tour through Gwangjang Market in Jongno, structured as a stamp-rally challenge that works through the market''s signature street foods, with a souvenir folded into the format. This is Klook''s own tour, booked directly through that platform.

With a 4.9 rating across 179 reviews, and guides repeatedly praised for their local knowledge and warmth, it offers a structured way to take on the market rather than guessing on your own. Set aside a half day for the full route.', 4.9, 179, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Gwangjang%20Market%20Half-Day%20Street%20Food%20Experience%20%EC%A2%85%EB%A1%9C/%EA%B4%91%EC%9E%A5%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EA%B4%91%EC%9E%A5%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20%EB%B0%98%EB%82%98%EC%A0%88%20%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EB%A6%AC%ED%8A%B8%ED%91%B8%EB%93%9C%20%ED%88%AC%EC%96%B4', true),
('gwangjang-market-half-day-vegan-food-tour', 'Gwangjang Vegan Food Tour', '광장시장 반나절 비건 푸드투어', 'food_tour'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Jongno', '서울 종로구 광장시장', 'Vegan food tour', 'Half-day vegan food tour through Gwangjang Market.', null, 'plant-based eaters exploring Gwangjang Market', 'Plant-based visitors get a route of their own through Gwangjang Market with this half-day tour, which currently holds a 5.0 rating. The premise is straightforward: a guided walk through the Jongno market focused entirely on vegan food.

Published details are otherwise limited, so confirm the current lineup of stops — and any dietary specifics that matter to you — directly when booking.', 5, null, null, null, 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Gwangjang%20Market%20Half-Day%20Vegan%20Food%20Tour%20%EC%A2%85%EB%A1%9C/%EA%B4%91%EC%9E%A5%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EA%B4%91%EC%9E%A5%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%A5%20%EB%B0%98%EB%82%98%EC%A0%88%20%EB%B9%84%EA%B1%B4%20%ED%91%B8%EB%93%9C%ED%88%AC%EC%96%B4', true),
('absolute-seoul-pub-crawl-hongdae-itaewon', 'Absolute Seoul Pub Crawl', '앱솔루트 서울 펍크롤', 'food_tour'::place_category, 'experience'::place_entry_type, 'Hongdae', '홍대(목·토·일) / 이태원(금)', 'Nightlife pub crawl', 'High-energy pub crawl with hosts who mix an international crowd — Hongdae most nights, Itaewon on Fridays.', 'With a 4.8 rating across 263 reviews, the crawl is praised for local hosts who run the night with real energy and pull travelers of many nationalities into one group.', 'meeting fellow travelers on a night out', 'Absolute Seoul Pub Crawl runs on a fixed weekly rhythm: Hongdae on Thursdays, Saturdays, and Sundays, and Itaewon on Fridays. Local hosts keep the energy high and mix travelers of many nationalities into one group — reviewers describe it as much a way to meet fellow travelers as a bar tour.

The crawl has a website at seoulpubcrawl.com and an Instagram account at @absolutekorea; check which district is on before you head out, since the night''s location depends on the day of the week.', 4.8, 263, 'https://seoulpubcrawl.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/absolutekorea', 'https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Absolute%20Seoul%20Pub%20Crawl%20%28Hongdae/Itaewon%29%20%ED%99%8D%EB%8C%80/%EC%9D%B4%ED%83%9C%EC%9B%90%20Seoul', 'https://map.naver.com/p/search/%EC%95%B1%EC%86%94%EB%A3%A8%ED%8A%B8%20%EC%84%9C%EC%9A%B8%20%ED%8E%8D%ED%81%AC%EB%A1%A4', true),
('olive-young-n-seongsu', 'Olive Young N Seongsu', '올리브영 N 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장7길 13', 'K-beauty flagship', 'Olive Young''s five-floor innovation flagship, opened in late 2024 near Seongsu Station — the chain''s biggest bet yet on what a K-beauty store can be.', 'It''s less a bigger branch than a lab for the brand''s next store format, with each floor built around a different way of shopping rather than just more shelves.', 'a one-stop overview of what''s trending across Korean beauty right now', 'Olive Young N Seongsu opened in November 2024 as the chain''s first entry in a new ''innovation store'' concept, spread across five floors near Exit 4 of Seongsu Station. Where a standard Olive Young branch is organized by product category, this flagship is organized by experience — different floors are built around different ways of browsing and testing K-beauty products.

As the format-setter for where Olive Young''s retail concept is headed next, it''s worth the detour even for travelers who''ve already been to a dozen branches elsewhere in Seoul.', null, null, 'https://www.oliveyoung.co.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/oliveyoung_official', null, null, false),
('amore-seongsu', 'Amore Seongsu', '아모레성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 아차산로11길 7', 'K-beauty flagship', 'Amorepacific''s flagship experience space in a converted repair shop — test 2,000+ products across 30+ brands, no checkout pressure.', 'It''s built as a showroom, not a store — plus free luggage lockers, which every carry-on traveler eventually thanks them for.', 'Trying the whole Amorepacific universe before you buy', 'Amore Seongsu occupies a former auto repair shop converted into Amorepacific''s group-wide showroom, letting visitors test products from more than 30 of the company''s brands in one open space rather than shopping brand by brand. With well over 2,000 products on hand, it''s built for exploration rather than a fast checkout.

Free luggage lockers make it a practical stop mid-itinerary, and the space sits alongside several other beauty and fashion flagships on Seongsu''s Yeonmujang-area streets.', null, null, 'https://global.amoremall.com/pages/about-amoreseongsu', 'https://www.instagram.com/amore_seongsu', null, null, false),
('tamburins-seongsu', 'Tamburins Seongsu', '탬버린즈 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장5길 8', 'Fragrance flagship', 'A raw-concrete flagship built around Tamburins'' perfumes, hand creams, and rotating art installations, on one of Seongsu''s original converted-warehouse streets.', 'The architecture is the draw as much as the products — the cave-like concrete interior has made it a fixture in Seongsu''s design-tourism circuit since it opened.', 'browsing niche Korean fragrance without a hard sell', 'Tamburins Seongsu is the fragrance and cosmetics brand''s flagship on Yeonmujang 5-gil, built inside a raw-concrete structure that leans as hard into architecture as it does into product. Alongside the brand''s perfumes, hand creams, and body care, the space regularly hosts art installations that change out the interior look.

It''s open daily from 11am to 9pm, a few minutes from Seongsu Station Exit 4, and works well paired with the other flagship stores clustered on the same block.', null, null, 'https://www.tamburins.com/en/store/korea/', 'https://www.instagram.com/tamburinsofficial', null, null, false),
('nonfiction-seongsu', 'Nonfiction Seongsu', '논픽션 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장길 8-1', 'Fragrance flagship', 'A minimalist showroom for Nonfiction''s fragrance and skincare line, with open counters built for unhurried testing rather than a quick grab-and-go.', 'The pared-back, gallery-like layout matches the brand''s whole aesthetic — it reads more like a design showroom than a retail counter.', 'sampling Nonfiction''s signature scents at your own pace', 'Nonfiction''s Seongsu store is one of more than ten global locations for the fragrance and skincare brand, but it''s the flagship showroom for Seoul. The interior favors open testing counters and a restrained material palette over dense product walls, in keeping with the brand''s minimalist identity.

It keeps daily hours from 11am to 8:30pm and sits a short walk from Tamburins and other Seongsu flagships, making it an easy stop on a fragrance-focused route through the neighborhood.', null, null, 'https://www.nonfiction.com/pages/stores', 'https://www.instagram.com/official.nonfiction', null, null, false),
('tirtir-seongsu', 'TIRTIR Seongsu', '티르티르 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장5길 7', 'K-beauty flagship', 'TIRTIR''s two-floor flagship, built around its cult-favorite cushion foundation shade range — five distinct zones for matching your exact tone before you buy.', 'The ''Shade Valley'' concept turns a task that''s usually a guessing game online — picking the right cushion shade — into something you can actually test in person.', 'finding your shade match among TIRTIR''s wide cushion foundation range', 'TIRTIR Seongsu opened in mid-2025 as the brand''s flagship, spread across a basement and ground floor near Seongsu Station on Yeonmujang 5-gil. The store is organized into five themed zones under a ''Shade Valley'' concept, built specifically around trying the brand''s wide range of cushion foundation shades in person.

The store passed its first anniversary with a dedicated event, a reasonable signal it''s a standing flagship rather than a short-lived promotional pop-up. Hours run 10:30am to 8:30pm daily.', null, null, 'https://tirtir.co.kr/brand/store.html', 'https://www.instagram.com/tirtir_official', null, null, false),
('amuse-seongsu', 'Amuse Seongsu', '어뮤즈 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장길 10-2', 'K-beauty flagship', 'Amuse''s all-pink ''Pink House'' flagship — a full brand-world showroom for its vegan, jelly-textured makeup line, opened in mid-2025.', 'It commits fully to one color story instead of splitting the difference, which makes it read as a genuine brand statement rather than a generic pop-up shell.', 'the most photographed makeup showroom in Seongsu right now', 'Amuse opened its Seongsu flagship — nicknamed ''Pink House'' — in June 2025, its second flagship store after an earlier Hongdae location. The roughly 200-square-meter space is built entirely around the brand''s signature pink and its vegan, jelly-textured makeup and skincare line.

Expect a dense photo-op interior alongside testing stations for Amuse''s core products; it''s a quick stop rather than a long browse, but a distinctive one on a Seongsu beauty crawl.', null, null, 'https://amusemakeup.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/amuse', null, null, false),
('fwee-seongsu', 'fwee Seongsu', '퓌 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수이로7가길 10', 'K-beauty flagship', 'fwee''s first offline store, nicknamed ''AGIT'' — built around testing its full lip-tint and pudding-pot color range in one blue-toned space.', 'Dozens of shades laid out for open testing is a genuinely useful format for a brand best known online for color range — you can actually compare them side by side here.', 'swatching fwee''s full lip color lineup in one visit', 'fwee AGIT Seongsu, opened in February 2024, is the makeup brand''s first permanent offline store after a run of pop-ups, including one at The Hyundai Seoul. The store leans into fwee''s signature blue on its exterior and gives shoppers open access to test dozens of lip product shades and the brand''s full pudding pot lineup.

It keeps year-round daily hours from 11am to 9pm and sits a short walk from several of Seongsu''s other beauty flagships, making it easy to fold into a same-day beauty-store route.', null, null, 'https://fwee.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/fwee_makeup', null, null, false),
('musinsa-standard-seongsu', 'Musinsa Standard Seongsu', '무신사 스탠다드 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장길 83', 'Fashion flagship', 'The physical storefront for Musinsa''s in-house basics label, letting you check sizing and fabric on pieces most travelers only know from the app.', 'It turns Korea''s biggest fashion platform from a screen into a fitting room — genuinely useful if you plan to keep shopping Musinsa''s app after you fly home.', 'checking Musinsa Standard sizing and fit before ordering more online', 'Musinsa Standard Seongsu is the two-floor retail store for Musinsa''s own basics line, part of a broader wave of offline stores the online platform has opened in the neighborhood alongside its larger Musinsa Megastore Seongsu. The space stocks minimalist, everyday casualwear in neutral colorways, the label''s signature look.

It''s open daily from 11am to 9pm with tax-free service for international visitors, making it a practical stop if you already shop the Musinsa app and want to check fit in person.', null, null, 'https://locations.musinsa.com/ko/stndss', 'https://www.instagram.com/musinsa.store', null, null, false),
('ader-error-seongsu', 'Ader Error Seongsu Space', '아더에러 성수 스페이스', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수이로 82', 'Fashion flagship', 'Ader Error''s flagship since 2020, renovated for the brand''s 10th anniversary into a chrome-and-glass, gallery-like two-floor space.', 'The renovation treats the store as an art installation first and a shop second, which fits a brand that''s always blurred the line between fashion and conceptual art.', 'seeing Ader Error''s off-kilter design language applied to a whole building, not just a rack of clothes', 'ADER Space has anchored Ader Error''s presence in Seongsu since 2020, and was fully renovated in late 2024 for the brand''s tenth anniversary under the theme ''FUTOURIST.'' The redesign leans into glass and chrome finishes with undulating interiors and futuristic fixtures across two floors, alongside the brand''s ready-to-wear and accessories.

Open daily from 1pm to 9pm, it''s one of the longer-standing flagships in the neighborhood rather than a newcomer, and rewards a slower browse over a quick in-and-out.', null, null, 'https://www.adererror.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/ader_error', null, null, false),
('lcdc-seoul', 'LCDC Seoul', 'LCDC 서울', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장17길 10', 'Select shop complex', 'A four-floor complex stacking a café, a multi-brand select shop, and several independent fashion labels under one roof — Seongsu''s version of a vertical mall.', 'Each floor has its own distinct identity instead of blending into one generic retail floor, so it rewards working your way up rather than just hitting the ground level.', 'browsing several independent Korean fashion labels without hopping between separate stores', 'LCDC Seoul stacks a ground-floor café (Cafe Ephemera) with a curated multi-brand select shop on the second floor and several independent labels — including Doors, Geulwoll, and Apoteka Soul — sharing the third, plus a jewelry-and-accessories floor above. The building itself, a converted structure on Yeonmujang 17-gil, is part of the draw alongside what''s inside it.

Hours vary a little by floor, roughly 10am to 9pm depending on the tenant, with valet parking available — useful given how spread out Seongsu''s flagship stores are.', null, null, 'https://lcdc-seoul.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/lcdc.seoul', null, null, false),
('eql-grove-seongsu', 'EQL Grove', '이큐엘 그로브', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장15길 11', 'Select shop', 'EQL''s offline entry point into Seongsu, an ''editorial forest'' select shop that brings the online platform''s curated fashion picks into a physical space with rotating local brand collaborations.', 'It functions as a community space as much as a shop — the rotating collaborations with local Seongsu brands give it a reason to check back on repeat visits.', 'discovering smaller Korean labels alongside EQL''s own curated picks', 'EQL Grove brought the online curated-fashion platform EQL into a physical Seongsu storefront, styled as an ''editorial forest'' that showcases items previously only available through the app. Beyond straightforward shopping, the space runs themed promotions and collaborations with other local Seongsu brands.

It''s open daily from 11am to 8pm, closed on Korean public holidays, and works well as a stop for travelers who want a curated, editor''s-pick alternative to the bigger flagship stores nearby.', null, null, 'https://www.eqlstore.com/special/13747/view', 'https://www.instagram.com/eql_space', null, null, false),
('matin-kim-seongsu', 'Matin Kim Seongsu', '마뗑킴 성수', 'shop'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장3길 9', 'Fashion flagship', 'Matin Kim''s Seongsu flagship for the label''s oversized, Y2K-leaning streetwear — one of several Seoul stores, but the one built as a full brand-world showroom.', 'It''s one of Matin Kim''s larger physical footprints, worth the trip if you already follow the brand''s fast-moving online drops and want to check fit for yourself.', 'trying on Matin Kim''s oversized silhouettes in person before buying online', 'Matin Kim runs several storefronts across Seongsu, and this flagship on Yeonmujang 3-gil is the label''s main showroom for the neighborhood, alongside smaller branch and special-edition stores nearby. The brand is known for oversized, Y2K-inflected streetwear that moves quickly through frequent online drops.

Seeing the fit and fabric in person is the main draw here, since Matin Kim''s popularity online means pieces can sell out fast — a fitting-room visit is a low-risk way to confirm sizing before committing to a purchase.', null, null, 'https://matinkim.com/about', 'https://www.instagram.com/matinkim_magazine', null, null, false),
('onion-seongsu', 'Onion Seongsu', '어니언 성수', 'cafe'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 아차산로9길 8', 'Warehouse café & bakery', 'The original Onion — a converted factory turned bakery café that''s widely credited with kicking off Seongsu''s transformation into Seoul''s café district.', 'It predates most of the cafés that copied its look, and it still bakes well enough to be worth the visit even without the exposed-brick backdrop.', 'warehouse-industrial atmosphere plus a genuinely strong bakery counter', 'Onion Seongsu occupies a former factory building and is often credited as the café that put Seongsu-dong on the map as a destination neighborhood, well before the area filled with flagship fashion stores. The bakery counter, not just the industrial-chic interior, is the reason regulars keep returning — bread and pastries sell out on busy days.

It opens earlier than most Seongsu cafés, from 8am on weekdays and 10am on weekends, both running until 10pm — useful if you want to beat the crowds that build later in the day.', null, null, 'http://onionkr.com/', 'https://www.instagram.com/cafe.onion', null, null, false),
('daelim-changgo', 'Daelim Changgo', '대림창고', 'cafe'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수이로 78', 'Warehouse café-gallery', 'A former 1970s rice mill turned cavernous café and gallery — one of the buildings that defined Seongsu''s industrial-chic look before it became a shopping destination.', 'The scale is the point — few Seongsu cafés give you this much raw, unrenovated volume to sit in, and the rotating gallery shows give you a reason to return.', 'a huge, high-ceilinged café space that doubles as an art and event venue', 'Daelim Changgo occupies a red-brick building that operated as a rice mill in the 1970s, since converted into a combined café and gallery that keeps much of the original warehouse structure intact. The space regularly hosts art exhibitions and events alongside its regular café service.

It''s open daily from 11am to 10pm, a short walk from Onion Seongsu, and the two are commonly visited back-to-back as the neighborhood''s original warehouse-café landmarks.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/daelimchanggo_gallery', null, null, false),
('mesh-coffee', 'Mesh Coffee', '메쉬커피', 'cafe'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 서울숲길 43', 'Specialty espresso bar', 'A compact, takeout-only hand-drip specialty bar near Seoul Forest — no seating, just a tight focus on the coffee itself.', 'Dropping seating entirely lets it focus purely on the brew — a useful counterpoint if you''ve spent the day in Seongsu''s photo-op cafés and just want good coffee, fast.', 'a quick, high-quality coffee stop on the walk to or from Seoul Forest', 'Mesh Coffee is a small, takeout-only specialty bar between Seoul Forest and Ttukseom Station, built around hand-drip coffee rather than a sit-down café experience. There''s no indoor seating, so it works best as a stop on the way to or from Seoul Forest park rather than a destination to linger at.

Weekday hours run 10am to 6pm; the matcha latte and Americano are the most-mentioned menu items, and its small footprint means it can get busy quickly around peak café-hopping hours.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/meshcoffee', null, null, false),
('in-the-pink-seongsu', 'In The Pink Seongsu', '인더핑크 성수', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수동', 'English-first personal color analysis', 'An English-first personal color studio in Seongsu, run by a bilingual founder who has draped 9,000-plus clients through a 350-plus-swatch process.', 'Founder Nicole built the entire booking flow, and the FAQ that explains bare-face draping, around clients who don''t speak Korean — down to the wording of the questions people actually ask before a session.', 'travelers who want the whole session — booking form to drape to breakdown — handled comfortably in English', 'In The Pink is a personal color studio in Seongsu run by Nicole, a certified color consultant and fashion stylist who has led personal color workshops abroad through the Korean Cultural Center, including stops in Hungary, the UK, the Czech Republic, Italy, and Spain. Sessions center on a bare-face draping process using more than 350 fabric swatches to identify a client''s undertone, then extend into recommendations for makeup shades, hairstyle and color, glasses frames, and fabric choices.

Booking runs through a form-and-email flow rather than a walk-in counter, with 1:1 sessions lasting about 80 minutes and paired sessions running longer — all explained in English from the FAQ onward, which is unusual for the format in Seongsu. The studio''s exact address isn''t published online; it''s shared directly with clients once a booking is confirmed.', null, null, 'https://www.inthepink-color.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/in_the_pink_color', null, null, false),
('ccl-color-lab-seongsu', 'CCL Color Image Convergence Lab', 'CCL 컬러이미지융합연구소', 'personal_color'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 성수이로 66, 서울숲 드림타워 711호', 'Personal color diagnosis & consulting', 'A personal-color and image-consulting lab near Seoul Forest, run out of its own Seongsu studio with a full program menu from color draping to body-frame styling.', 'CCL also runs its own academy arm and holds patent registrations for its diagnostic tools, so the person draping you has typically also trained other colour consultants in the method.', 'a deeper consulting menu — color, body-frame styling, and makeup — under one roof rather than a single-service session', 'CCL (컬러이미지융합연구소) runs its personal color studio out of the Seoul Forest Dream Tower in Seongsu, a short walk from Seoul Forest itself. Alongside its core personal color consulting program, the lab offers a men''s-focused diagnosis track, body-frame and fit styling, makeup consulting, and color therapy sessions.

What sets it apart from single-session studios nearby is the academy side of the business — CCL holds its own patent registrations for diagnostic tools and issues its own counselor certifications through a dedicated training arm. Sessions can be booked through its Instagram (@cclcolor_official) or arranged directly through the studio.', null, null, 'https://cclcolor.co.kr', 'https://www.instagram.com/cclcolor_official', null, null, false),
('5x5-nail-studio-seongsu', '5x5 Nail Studio Seongsu', '오오네일 성수', 'nail_lash'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 상원2길 5, 2층', 'Contemporary nail art studio', 'A high-following nail art studio in Seongsu known for nature-inspired custom designs — marble, stone, and watercolor motifs — booked entirely through Instagram.', 'The studio keeps separate accounts for its class offerings and design archive, a level of documentation that''s closer to a working design studio than a typical walk-in nail shop.', 'elaborate custom nail art booked in advance, with English-speaking staff on hand', '5x5 Nail Studio (오오네일) runs two Seoul locations, one in Seongsu and one in Yeonnam, and has built a large following around nature-inspired nail art — marble, stone-texture, and watercolor motifs among its signature styles. Appointments, which typically run about an hour to ninety minutes depending on the design, are arranged through Instagram DM or KakaoTalk rather than a booking site.

English-speaking staff support the international clients who make up a large share of its bookings, and the studio maintains sister accounts for its class offerings and design archive — worth a browse before messaging to book, since custom pieces are usually chosen from a reference photo.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/5x5nailstudio', null, null, false),
('dakyo-nail-seongsu', 'Dakyo Nail Seongsu', '다교네일 성수', 'nail_lash'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장15길 11, 305호', 'Nail art studio', 'The Seongsu branch of the Dakyo Nail family, a K-pop-adjacent nail art studio with its own account and following distinct from the brand''s Hannam and Apgujeong locations.', 'Being the Seongsu outpost of a multi-branch brand means near-daily fresh design uploads on its own account — a useful scroll for style references before you message to book.', 'trend-driven, idol-inspired nail art in the style Dakyo Nail is known for', 'Dakyo Nail Seongsu (다교네일 성수) is one of several branches under the Dakyo Nail name, a nail art brand also operating in Hannam-dong and — separately from this Seongsu shop — Apgujeong. The Seongsu location runs its own Instagram account distinct from the brand''s main and representative accounts, posting frequent updates on current nail art designs.

As with most Seongsu nail studios of this type, booking runs through Instagram DM or a linked Kakao channel rather than a website, and the shop sits in a commercial building on Yeonmujang 15-gil in the heart of the neighborhood''s studio cluster.', null, null, null, 'https://www.instagram.com/dakyonail_cute', null, null, false),
('soonsiki-seongsu', 'Soonsiki Seongsu', '순시키 성수', 'salon'::place_category, 'place'::place_entry_type, 'Seongsu', '서울 성동구 연무장3길 17, 4·5층', 'English-friendly hair salon', 'The Seongsu branch of Soonsiki, a multi-location Seoul hair chain built around English-friendly service for international guests.', 'Soonsiki brands its English-friendly service and multi-branch consistency directly on its own site rather than leaving it to a DM negotiation, which is unusual for a Seongsu salon at this scale.', 'a full-service cut, color, or perm handled by a chain that markets its English-friendliness up front', 'Soonsiki Seongsu (순시키헤어 성수 샤미즈점) is one of four Seoul locations run under the Soonsiki name, occupying the 4th and 5th floors of a building on Yeonmujang 3-gil, alongside sibling branches in Hongdae. The chain has built its identity around serving international guests specifically, branding itself as English-friendly across its locations.

Booking runs through the salon''s own site or its Instagram (@soonsiki.official), and the Seongsu branch keeps the same Wednesday–Sunday, 10am–7pm schedule as the rest of the chain, closed Mondays and Tuesdays.', null, null, 'https://www.soonsiki.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/soonsiki.official', null, null, false)
